{"tid":1723632,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"如果中國出現黑死病","createTime":"2019-11-15T08:44:43.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-15T08:45:46.000Z","uid":149342,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"f999c6f5af429e58fabc5af1212bfd614c0169c5","tid":1723632,"uid":149342,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T08:44:43.000Z","msg":"如果中國出現黑死病<br />\n咁中國人均支啲呸就會升一倍<br />\n<br />\n暗黑流星拳 Black Ryu Sei Ken<br />\n暗黑天馬最大奧義，包含大量的劇毒素，能夠穿透聖衣擊中對手的身體。當暗黑流星拳擊出後，在毒素作用下，對手被擊中的的地方血液變得混濁，然後身體上出現黑色斑點，黑色斑點會逐漸擴大，當對方身上的黑斑覆蓋整個身體時即會死亡，所以暗黑流星拳又名「黑死拳」。"},{"pid":"3d6a81c7ad0019715e210d0ec58fa492e19039dc","tid":1723632,"uid":147916,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T08:45:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/67rehV1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F67rehV1.jpg&h=1f4d5a27&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3410bf4179f2fdae05e3a97588d3906da07d7bd1","tid":1723632,"uid":249263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T08:45:46.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: gold;\">出門之前 rt like reply</span><br />\nTwitter組會keep住更新<br />\n幫手retweet<br />\n㩒入👉<a href=\"https://t.me/TwitterHelpBot\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FTwitterHelpBot&d=DwP82Rd5Y8BeeioconDBYad04xtnDtF9LgqILkRy7NQ%3D&h=e8c2bf54\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/TwitterHelpBot</a><br />\n然後打 /task 攞任務<br />\n<br />\nSenator Scott 幫香港人出聲<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">Rt + like </span><br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/senrickscott/status/1195147582609252353?s=21\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fsenrickscott%2Fstatus%2F1195147582609252353%3Fs%3D21&d=DwP82Rd5Y8BeeioconDBYad04xtnDtF9LgqILkRy7NQ%3D&h=79a946d5\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fsenrickscott%2Fstatus%2F1195147582609252353%3Fs%3D21&h=37d03fec\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/senrickscott/status/11951475